name: Sam Graves
speech: Mr. GRAVES. Madam Chair, I have an amendment at the desk.  The Acting CHAIR. The Clerk will designate the amendment.  The text of the amendment is as follows:  In division E, strike section 106.  The Acting CHAIR. Pursuant to ', House Resolution 436, ", the gentleman  from Louisiana (Mr. Graves) and a Member opposed each will control 5  minutes.  The Chair recognizes the gentleman from Louisiana.
